    rdau:P61101 "<a href='https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Leir_of_Britain'>Wikipedia</a>, katsottu 17.12.2025 (Leir of Britain: Leir was a legendary king of the Britons whose story was recounted by Geoffrey of Monmouth in his pseudohistorical 12th-century History of the Kings of Britain. According to Geoffrey's genealogy of the British dynasty, Leir reigned around the 8th century BC, around the time of the founding of Rome. The story was modified and retold by William Shakespeare in his Jacobean tragedy King Lear.)"@fi ;
