    rdau:P61101 "<a href='https://prabook.com/web/gilbert_antony.wood/189392'>Prabook</a>, katsottu 30.12.2025 (Gilbert Antony Wood, New Zealand Political science educator. President Dunedin branches New Zealand Institute International Affairs, 1978-1979, Association University Teachers, 1989-1990, New Zealand Institute Public Administration, 1988-1993, New Zealand Political Studies Association, 1981-1982. Member Rotary (president Dunedin North club 1990-1991). ... born on October 17, 1936 in Wellington, New Zealand. ... Tutor, U. Otago, 1960-1961; assistant lecturer, U. Otago, 1962-1965; temporary lecturer, U. Otago, 1966; senior lecturer, U. Otago, 1974-1978; associate professor political studies, U. Otago, since 1978; postdoctoral fellow, U. Cambridge, England, 1966-1968; senior lecturer, U. Auckland, New Zealand, 1968-1974.)"@fi,
